{
  "stem": "24195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When my father and his, his brother, who was the chairman of-- was a, a urologist and was chairman of the urology department of the University of Berlin Medical School.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Eugen Joseph.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they were-- they-- my father wouldn't drive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he had a driver's license, but he always drove in a chauffeured-driven limousine in those days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was an incident apparently that was around 1929, 1930, '31.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were taking a ride out in the vicinity of Germany, around Berlin and just-- you know, on a, a pleasure ride.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the driver got lost on the-- in-- on the highway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- there were some farmers working in the fields nearby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It must have been in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he motioned one of the farmers to come over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the farmer came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he, he looked-- and he was going to ask him, you know, for directions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the farmer didn't answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he looked into the back of the limo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he saw my parents, and my, my father's brother and his wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he just says, Jews, and walked away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So certainly there-- that was-- even before Hitler came to power, there was a-- Hitler found very willing subjects when he-- you know, that opinion of people that were already, you know, formed about the Jewish persecution.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, my, my wife's-- my uncle, my father's brother, was a-- had a very tragic ending, which-- he was so despondent when he got his letter that he could no longer-- he was-- he had a large private practice.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he, you know, got the notification that he was-- his license was withdrawn, he just could never mentally recover from it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
